                <p class="text-base text-violet-950 ml-5">To test the safety and functionality of an investigational medical device that does not yet have its predicate device, manufacturers must carry out a post-marketing clinical investigation (which may include additional drug-device interactions, safety studies, investigations intended to support use under the approved indication, such as mortality or morbidity studies, etc.).</p>
