                            <li class="mb-2 font-poppinssemibold">Step 4: <span class="font-poppinsregular">Send in the application cost. After reviewing the application, the CDSCO might ask for more details.</span></li>
                            <li class="mb-2 font-poppinssemibold">Step 5: <span class="font-poppinsregular">Your device will receive an import license from CDSCO after they approve it.</span></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
